r />\n4 &#8211; Browser cache: enabled<br />\n5 &#8211; Lazy Load images: None<br />\n6 &#8211; Late initialization: enabled<br />\n7 &#8211; Minify &#8211; enabled with exclusion of mfunc and mclude</p>\n<p>In wp-config.php:<br />\n<code>define(&#039;W3TC_DYNAMIC_SECURITY&#039;, &#039;FRAGMENT_CACHING&#039;);</code></p>\n<p>In Newspaper theme template, file footer.php, this is the code:</p>\n<pre><code>&lt;!-- mfunc FRAGMENT_CACHING --&gt;\necho date(&#039;Y-m-d H:i:s&#039;);\n&lt;!-- /mfunc FRAGMENT_CACHING --&gt;</code></pre>\n<p>When i empty cache and reload the page, works.<br />\nBut when i reload again, shows this:<br />\n<code>echo date(&#039;Y-m-d H:i:s&#039;);</code></p>\n<p>I&#8217;ve try some variations like:</p>\n<pre><code>&lt;!--mfunc &lt;?php echo W3TC_DYNAMIC_SECURITY; ?&gt; --&gt;\necho date(&#039;Y-m-d H:i:s&#039;);\n&lt;!--/mfunc &lt;?php echo W3TC_DYNAMIC_SECURITY; ?&gt; --&gt;</code></pre>\n<p>But none of this works.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/topic/fragment-cache-not-working/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">This topic</a> is a similar problem, but there&#8217;s no solution.</p>\n<p>Is there something i forgot to setting?</p>\n<p>Thanks!</p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~4/flM_fICezIM\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"danielsaal\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://wordpress.org/support/topic/page-fragment-cache-doesnt-work/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:15;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base